title: Sony's Car & Toyota's City ft. Austin Evans: CES Part 2
description:
Sony unveils a car and Toyota is planning a city? Has CES gone totally off the rails with announcements? We're joined by fellow tech YouTuber Austin Evans to discuss several of the crazy and futuristic ideas companies bring to CES that may or may not ever actually hit the retail market.
